16th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 12 Highlights

For the third of the Pyrennean stages, the riders have a really tough day in store on stage 12 - 195km and four summits to cross, including the finish atop the fearsome Plateau de Beille. There will be nowhere to hide today, and the GC contenders will be pushing each other to the limit in their bids for success. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
